doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Mail
        style
            include ../Css/Welcome.css
            include ../Css/Header.css
    body 
        main 
            div.headerSection 
                div.imageHeader
                    img(src="https://i.postimg.cc/yNHdv7tw/African-woman-with-colorful-shopping.jpg", alt="", srcset="")
            div.textHeader
                    h1 Shoplet 
                    p Get your favorite product at your doorstep with one click.
            div.messageText 
                p Hey #{UserName}, 
                p.                
                    Welcome to Shoplet your ultimate destination for all things shopping! We're thrilled to have you with us and can't wait for you to explore our vast range of products.

                br 
                p.
                    Whether you're looking for the latest fashion, must-have gadgets, or something special to spruce up your home, Shoplet has it all. Plus, our exclusive deals and offers are just the beginning of the amazing perks you'll enjoy as part of the Shoplet community.
                br
                p.
                    See you around,
                    The Shoplet Team at Shoplet.
         

